---
title: Pan-Seared Duck & Caramelised Onion Sauce with Potato Mash & Sautéed Baby Broccoli
description: Spice up your Sunday roast with decadent duck breast and all the trimmings: from the luxurious mash to the charred greens and
a sweet and savoury caramelised onion sauce, everyone will want seconds.
